// item_topic You has visited this place. Convo works with the help of Facebook\'s API. It collects certain pieces of information from users\' public profiles, limited to the users\' name, profile picture, information on their tagged places, the pages they like, and friends who are also on the app. How does Convo work? How Freestyle Mode Works Choose a total time for the game, and swipe the cards at your leisure until time runs out. You can always play again! How Timed Mode Works Choose the number of cards you\'d like to talk about and the amount of time per card. You can always swipe a card before the timer ends. How Basic Mode Works Use basic mode to discuss some general topics with anyone, regardless of whether they\'re your facebook friend or have the app. DISCLAIMER!!! This deck of cards is based off of the NYT article on 36 questions that two people can discuss to fall in love. THIS DECK IS GUARANTEED TO MAKE YOU TWO FALL IN LOVE SO USE WITH CAUTION.
